      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SWIFT DRAGON (1) ran above expectations, winning in good style over 1200m in the QTIS JEWEL (2yo) at Gold Coast. Went close in another rich Open 2 at Eagle Farm prior, and Wiggins sticks aboard. Well placed to take this out. APOSTLE (2) led and broke through for his Maiden win over 1300m at Eagle Farm last time. Is lightly raced and has plenty of scope for improvement. BOOMELLI (4) presents off a first-up win here over 1000m. Will appreciate the big weight drop and Ben Thompson is reunited. In the top metro stable and should be involved in the finish. WORTHTHEADMISSION (6) debuts for the Munce yard. She's shown talent at the trials and keep a close eye on the betting.",
